{"tid":1424651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日話你有雷射槍，聽日話你買雷神鎚","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:53:21.000Z","uid":89,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"61cd2451d6501cf2ee67ca5054bd566d9bddcf76","tid":1424651,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:16:40.000Z","msg":"明顯警察就係想無風起浪，係警署門口先黎個近距離對答，好似好貼地，但答d垃圾，引起市民前線憤怒，再派防暴，速龍捉人<br />\n<br />\n聽日4點鐘許sir又有新野講<br />\n<br />\n講下今晚有班人衝警署，好激進，有關雷射槍的野就避談，唔清楚，唔知道，返去查下再答你，<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係放重點係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">深水埗區暴徒好激進</span></span><br />\n<br />\n為左保護深水埗區市民安全，決定派出防暴，速龍盡快控制局面<br />\n<br />\n聽日後日又可以捉人話見到可疑人士買雷神鎚，買美國隊長盾，買左套iron man套裝<br />\n<br />\n不要被敵人牽著走，最終變成佔中2.0"},{"pid":"1d1bb12c504e3d1b56ac751011830c02ed835f76","tid":1424651,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"自推睇唔過眼"},{"pid":"8068ff4a5ab929ef57d3bd079c98f82dd43b2367","tid":1424651,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:17:09.000Z","msg":"自推睇唔過眼"},{"pid":"b20c079ee9182b368a81c4b6dbdc00c6d1ad4ea7","tid":1424651,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"自推睇唔過眼"},{"pid":"ac91b0f38c2d87be173dd73ac1b009bc85131c26","tid":1424651,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"自推睇唔過眼"},{"pid":"d3d62dce317e0f595e3a025468ac60cf8b921453","tid":1424651,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67b0520e410b303d3fb8189d5f0309496f79fca","tid":1424651,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96699cb5a5bd0cb278929b1013d2205f0f2076f","tid":1424651,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c